Title: Let It Be, Leave It Alone
---
will lead you up above the Great Brilliance, to the source of the
Perfect Yang; I will guide you through the Dark and Mvsterious Gate, to
the source of the Perfect Yin. Heaven and earth have their controllers,
the yin and yang their storehouses. You have only to take care and
guard your own body; these other things will of themselves grow sturdy.
As for myself, I guard this unity, abide in this harmony, and therefore
I have kept myself alive for twelve hundred years, and never has my
body suffered any decay."
